.@DeptVetAffairs' RANGE programs offer outpatient services for veterans in rural areas living with mental illnesses.

@RepCindyAxne's Sgt. Ketchum Rural Veterans Mental Health Act – signed into law this week – will open 3 more RANGE programs to reach more veterans in rural areas. https://twitter.com/VetAffairsDems/status/1394376954212671490 QT @VetAffairsDems Sergeant Ketchum was a veteran from Iowa who died by suicide after failing to receive treatment for his PTSD.

@RepCindyAxne's bipartisan bill honors his memory with action by working prevent similar tragedies for rural veterans – a group at increased risk of dying by suicide. ⬇️ http://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1394376761102770184/pu/img/1U6Oo2lLPsComgRW.jpg https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/1394376761102770184/pu/vid/480x270/T8T01dIUxK3pBMzn.mp4?tag=12

